transcript: Hi, my name is Sarah Johnson. I'm reaching out because I really need help. I lost my job three months ago due to company downsizing, and I've been struggling to keep up with rent and bills. I'm currently living in Denver, Colorado. I have two young children, ages 5 and 7, and we're at risk of losing our apartment. I need help with housing costs and food for my kids. I've been applying for jobs every day, but it's been really hard. My email is sarah.johnson@email.com and my phone number is 303-555-1234. I'm hopeful that with some support, I can get back on my feet and provide for my family. Thank you for listening to my story.
